26 (5) Unless otherwise directed by order of a court of competent
27 jurisdiction, a financial institution may extend the duration under
28 subsection (4) of this section based on a reasonable belief that the
29 financial exploitation of a vulnerable adult or senior adult may continue
30 to occur or continue to be attempted.
31 (6) A financial institution and its bank holding company, if any,
